mber1'>Изображение</td>						<td><input type = "file" name = "photo" acept = "image/jpeg"></td>					</tr>				</table>				</fieldset>				<input type = "submit" name = "add" value = "Добавить" class="buttonw">		</form>		</div><?	}?>